@startuml ACR-QA-Pipeline-Stages
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
'  ACR-QA  v4.0.0  —  12-Stage Processing Pipeline
'  Ahmed Mahmoud Abbas  (222101213)  ·  KSIU  ·  CSE494  ·  2026
'──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName  "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize  10
skinparam shadowing        false

skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor        #E8EDF4
  BorderColor            #002654
  BorderThickness        2
  FontSize               10
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF3BF
  DiamondBorderColor     #C9A84C
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color     #002654
  FontColor #444444
  FontSize  9
  Thickness 1.5
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor     #C9A84C
  FontSize        9
}

skinparam legend {
  BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
  BorderColor     #CED4DA
  FontSize        9
}

start

'────────────────────────── STAGE 0 ──────────────────────────
:⓪  **Rate Limit & Job Init**
─────────────────────────────────
Redis token-bucket check
POST /v1/scan → 202 Accepted
Celery task enqueued · run ID returned;

note right
  API returns immediately
  Worker picks up async
end note

'────────────────────────── STAGE 1 ──────────────────────────
:①  **Repository Ingestion**
──────────────────────────────
Validate path · detect languages
(.py / .ts / .go extension scan)
PostgreSQL: UPDATE run SET status=RUNNING;

'────────────────────────── STAGE 2 ──────────────────────────
fork
  :Python Adapter
  Ruff · Bandit · Semgrep
  Vulture · Radon · jscpd;
fork again
  :JavaScript / TS Adapter
  ESLint-security · Semgrep
  npm audit · jscpd;
fork again
  :Go Adapter
  gosec · staticcheck
  Semgrep;
fork again
  :Cross-language
  Secrets Detector
  TruffleHog · Trivy;
end fork

note right
  Stage 2 — 12+ tools
  all run in parallel
  subprocess + thread pool
end note

'────────────────────────── STAGE 3 ──────────────────────────
:③a  **Normalise → CanonicalFinding**
──────────────────────────────────────
map to canonical schema (file / line / severity)
apply config filter · scope exclusions (≈15% eliminated);

:③b  **Triage Memory Lookup**
──────────────────────────────
check learned-suppression table
apply per-repo suppression rules;

:③c  **Cross-Tool Deduplication**
───────────────────────────────────
2-pass: location hash + rule hash
merge overlapping findings from different tools;

:③d  **Intra-Procedural Taint Analysis**
─────────────────────────────────────────
AST BFS from TAINT_SOURCES → TAINT_SINKS
confidence = max(0.4, 0.95 − 0.1·(h−1));

:③e  **Call-Graph Reachability**
──────────────────────────────────
BFS from Flask/FastAPI routes · Celery tasks · __main__
max_depth = 5;

if (finding reachable?) then (yes)
else (no — dead code)
  :Apply −20 confidence penalty
  (retained for audit, deprioritised);
endif

:③f  **Per-Rule Cap + Sort**
─────────────────────────────
cap max findings per rule
sort by confidence descending;

'────────────────────────── STAGE 4 ──────────────────────────
:④  **Five-Signal Confidence Scoring**
──────────────────────────────────────
severity · category · tool_reliability
rule_specificity · fix_validation
multi-tool bonus (+5) → C ∈ [0, 100];

if (C ≥ 30 ?) then (yes — keep)
else (no — soft-suppress)
  :Mark deprioritised
  (visible in dashboard, ranked last);
endif

:⑤  **RAG Enrichment**
────────────────────────
dict_lookup(canonical_rule_id) → O(1)
prompt Groq LLaMA-3.3-70B × 3 independent runs
N-gram entropy filter  τ = 3.2 bits
store in llm_explanations (full provenance);

note right
  97.1 % overall precision
  100 % security-class precision
  100 % enrichment rate
end note

:⑤b  **Post-Quantum Attestation**
───────────────────────────────────
ECDSA-P256 signature
CRYSTALS-Dilithium3 signature
Sigstore / Fulcio OIDC keyless signing;

'────────────────────────── STAGE 5 ──────────────────────────
:⑥  **Supply Chain · SCA · CBoM**
───────────────────────────────────
pip-audit · npm audit (CVE mapping)
CBoM: inventory 62 cryptographic primitives
flag NIST PQC deprecated algorithms;

'────────────────────────── STAGE 6 ──────────────────────────
:⑦  **Quality Gate**
──────────────────────
evaluate .acrqa.yml thresholds
PASS / FAIL per severity bucket
emit gate_result to CI runner;

'────────────────────────── STAGE 7 ──────────────────────────
:⑧  **Output Delivery**
────────────────────────
JSON · SARIF · Markdown
persist all findings to PostgreSQL
POST GitHub check-run + PR inline comments;

stop

legend top right
  |= Stage Group   |= Layer                          |
  |<back:#E8EDF4>  ⓪–①  </back>| Rate Limit + Ingestion       |
  |<back:#C8D8F0>  ②–③  </back>| Tool Execution + Normalise   |
  |<back:#FFF3BF>  ④–⑤  </back>| Scoring + AI Enrichment      |
  |<back:#D3F9D8>  ⑥–⑧  </back>| Supply Chain + Gate + Output |
end legend

@enduml
